Daily solar radiation during each of the growing seasons was obtained from China Meteorological Administration (http://www.cma.gov.cn) (Fig. 1). Daily Solar radiation in 2017 was calculated by Angstrom’s (1924) empirical formula:
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
